OL,3,CUkrainians mark independence day with
OL,4,Cpoignant Lockerbie ceremony
OL,6,FUkrainians in Dumfries and Galloway
OL,7,Fcame together on Saturday (24 August)
OL,8,Fto mark the country's independence day.
OL,10,FAt the Ukrainian POW Chapel, which
OL,11,Fsits just outside Lockerbie, those
OL,12,Fwith a Ukrainian heritage were joined
OL,13,Fby people who've recently left the
OL,14,Fcountry to plant a tree, and listen to
OL,15,Fspeeches.
