OL,3,CUkrainians mark independence day with
OL,4,Cpoignant Lockerbie ceremony
OL,6,F"It's a day when we should be
OL,7,Fcelebrating, but we're not," said
OL,8,FPeter Kormylo , who is an archivist
OL,9,Ffor Lockerbie Friends of Ukraine. "We
OL,10,Fare commiserating the fact that
OL,11,FUkraine is at war."
OL,13,FUkrainian independence is marked the
OL,14,Fday after 'Flag Day', which celebrates
OL,15,Fthe national flag. This was the third
OL,16,Findependence day commemorated since
OL,17,Fthe Russian invasion of Ukraine in
OL,18,F2022, which has since seen thousands
OL,19,Fof Ukrainians forced to flee their
OL,20,Fhomes.
