OL,3,CUkrainians mark independence day with
OL,4,Cpoignant Lockerbie ceremony
OL,6,FMany of the attendees at the Lockerbie
OL,7,Fevent have family still in the
OL,8,Fcountry. John Panczak, the Chairman of
OL,9,Fthe Friends, said he had relatives in
OL,10,FWestern Ukraine, "not necessarily tied
OL,11,Fup in the worst of what we're seeing
OL,12,Fin the East."
OL,14,FHe added: "Obviously we'd like to see
OL,15,Fan end to the war in Ukraine, but it
OL,16,Fseems, week by week, it's getting
OL,17,Ffurther away."
